    "description": "<p>You studies have granted you even greater knowledge of psionic secrets, granting the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You gain a +1 bonus to your Intelligence score to a maximum value of 20.</li><li>You immediately learn an additional psionic power of your choice. &nbsp;You must qualify for this power as normal.</li><li>Half your scholar levels count as esper levels for the purpose of your psionic reservoir.<br>Whenever a scholar ability requires you to expend a hit die, you may expend a psi die instead. &nbsp;Unlike normal such a psi die is always lost on being used.</li><li>When activating an augment on a psionic power, you may expend a hit die instead of a psi die. &nbsp;If an augment requires more than one psi die, only one of them may be replaced by a hit die.</li></ul>",
